I"Ž<p>The <code>filesize</code> sensor for displaying the size in MB of a file. Note that paths must be added to <a href="/docs/configuration/basic/">whitelist_external_dirs</a>.</p>
<h2>Configuration</h2>
<p>To enable the <code>filesize</code> sensor, add the following lines to your <code>configuration.yaml</code>:</p>
<pre><code class="language-yaml">sensor:
  - platform: filesize
    file_paths:
      - /config/home-assistant_v2.db
</code></pre>
<div class="config-vars">
  <h3><a class="title-link" name="configuration-variables" href="#configuration-variables"></a> Configuration Variables</h3>
  <dl class=''><dt><a class='title-link' name='file_paths' href='#file_paths'></a> file_paths</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='list'>list</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Required)</span><span class='description'><p>The absolute path to the file.</p>
</span></p></dd></dl>
</div>
